private void passage1_Init()
{
	base.Passages["Start2"] = new StoryPassage("Start2", new string[0], new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage1_Main));
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage1_Main()
{
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("MY FATHER'S WORK");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Choose a Scenario for ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.playtxt);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("players:");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("A Time of War", "Scenario2", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("Industry Forever", "Scenario3", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("Fear and Politics", "ScenarioBox-FOTU", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("The Cost of Disease", "Scenario5Start", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("For an explanation of how to use this Storybook,");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.link("click here.", "StoryBook", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.tracker = 0;
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private void passage2_Init()
{
	base.Passages["FearoftheUnknownStart"] = new StoryPassage("FearoftheUnknownStart", new string[]
	{
		"INTRO"
	}, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage2_Main));
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage2_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("GENERATION I: Fear of the Unknown");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Letter from ");
		if (this.Vars.players == 2)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 3)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 4)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC,
				this.Vars.nameD
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 5)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC,
				this.Vars.nameD,
				this.Vars.nameE
			});
		}
		this.Vars.randomname = this.Vars.randomplayer;
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.randomname);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("14 July, 1831.");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("It is with great reticence that I relay a grievous event which occurred upon my arrival. It is my hope that in penning these thoughts my mind will find solace from the foul images that have so firmly embedded themselves.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I will spare you the details of the journey to that dismal village to settle my deceased father's affairs. But upon entering its unpaved limits, my spouse drew my attention to several men and women galloping towards the town center, where there was a loud commotion and gathering of individuals. Intrigued by the local pageantry, I resolved to indulge my curiosity. I rapped my knuckles against the roof of the carriage and asked for the driver to turn towards the festivities.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("He did not respond to my insistence. Nor did he respond when I thrice repeated my command. Frustrated, I angled my head out of the carriage window in order to speak more firmly. That is when I spied the horrific source of his obstinate and wise decision. For the briefest of moments — though a moment long enough for it to be etched within my memory forever — I saw the source of the commotion: A crowd of people surrounded a tall wooden stage where, swinging slowly from a thick hemp noose, hung a youthful woman. Her lifeless eyes stared in my direction before her form was obscured by buildings.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("An irrational fear has gripped the populace. I swear it. The region is rife with superstitious traditions; traditions that do not mix well with the Church's rigid moral compass. When an individual from this close-knit community emerges from shuttered windows, they eye me as one would a foreigner, with sideways glances that make each excursion there insufferable. Accusations of witchcraft and voodooism erupt with increasing fervor, and paranoia weaves its tendrils into their minds.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Maybe this forced solitude will prove beneficial to my wits, as even amidst this clamor I find myself unnaturally focused. I have recently discovered my father's leather-bound journal and, while somewhat trite, I feel it has sparked something within me; a direction for my future studies, perhaps. Maybe it will offer some amusement in these trying times.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("Continue...", "ManiaSpecial", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.newspaper = "The " + this.Vars.townname + " " + this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
	{
		"Ledger",
		"Gazette",
		"Mercury",
		"Village Voice",
		"Examiner"
	});
	this.Vars.whpg = 0;
	this.Vars.fp10vp = 0;
	this.Vars.fpresearch2 = 0;
	this.Vars.fpsanity3 = 0;
	this.Vars.fpcreepy3 = 0;
	this.Vars.gen3pg = 0;
	this.Vars.plA = 0;
	this.Vars.plB = 0;
	this.Vars.plC = 0;
	this.Vars.plD = 0;
	this.Vars.plE = 0;
	this.Vars.onecount = 0;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage6_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("A Public Execution?");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.whpg = 0;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		if (this.Vars.players == 2)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 3)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 4)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC,
				this.Vars.nameD
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 5)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC,
				this.Vars.nameD,
				this.Vars.nameE
			});
		}
		this.Vars.randomname = this.Vars.randomplayer;
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.randomname);
		yield return base.text("'s Journal - ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("16 September, 1850. Romania.");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("It is nearing midnight now, and I struggle to find my words. Is this remorse I feel, or elation? Even as I was swept into the midst of the frightened crowd, watching the flames swirl upwards, I was spellbound by their savagery. I could not imagine that this paranoia would be exercised so bluntly!");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("It began over supper with my siblings: ");
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("The Blacksmith");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("- accused of practicing witchcraft - was carried past our brasserie to the steps of Town Hall. He wailed and protested his innocence, and when allowed use of his hands, he immediately accused Henriette, the town ");

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage13_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("GENERATION II: Hexes and Hysteria");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Letter from ");
		if (this.Vars.players == 2)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 3)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 4)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC,
				this.Vars.nameD
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 5)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC,
				this.Vars.nameD,
				this.Vars.nameE
			});
		}
		this.Vars.randomname = this.Vars.randomplayer;
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.randomname);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("April, 1863. Romania.");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I hope you will forgive the direct manner in which this letter is received. Due to recent events, I no longer entrust my correspondence to postal carriers and prefer to hire discrete private couriers. This message is meant for your eyes only and I will not allow those who so blatantly scheme against me an opportunity to uncover my motives!");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("This town has gone mad.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I have only just been situated these past few months with my spouse and close servants, and scarcely familiarized myself with the thatched-roofs and bucolic scenery, yet already I have seen the fires blaze at night, the screams of the damned, and the gibbet creaking under the weight of swinging bodies. The mob comes with torches in the evening and rips the accused from their residences. It appears that my parent's warnings proved true. The occult hysteria that they endured has returned in earnest! I fear that I may be next!");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Even my own cousins have begun to eye me like mongrel dogs, yearning for scraps. In their jealous mania, they wish to uncover my secrets and claim them for their own. I can see how they desire to place the blame upon me; to distract me from completing my family's important scientific work! It would break my heart to see ill come to them, yet if they continue in their provocations, I will not hesitate to unleash the fires of hell upon them.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("But I am secure in my ambitions. I have uncovered my true purpose. I will not succumb to fear. My secret work consumes my waking hours and I will stop at nothing to see it come to fruition!");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.path4 = "PEForeign";
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "CommemorativeIntro", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.brickvalue = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
	{
		1,
		2
	});
	if (this.Vars.kill == "butcher")
	{
		this.Vars.wsuspect = "Butcher's Apprentice";
	}
	else if (this.Vars.kill == "blacksmith")
	{
		this.Vars.wsuspect = "Blacksmith's Apprentice";
	}
	if (this.Vars.players == 2)
	{
		this.Vars.witch = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.wsuspect
		});
	}
	else if (this.Vars.players == 3)
	{
		this.Vars.witch = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.nameC,
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.nameC,
			this.Vars.wsuspect
		});
	}
	else if (this.Vars.players == 4)
	{
		this.Vars.witch = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.nameC,
			this.Vars.nameD
		});
	}
	else if (this.Vars.players == 5)
	{
		this.Vars.witch = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.nameC,
			this.Vars.nameD,
			this.Vars.nameE
		});
	}
	this.Vars.witAI = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
	{
		"Church",
		"Traveling Caravan",
		"Laborer's Union"
	});
	this.Vars.witAI2 = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
	{
		"Park",
		"Builder's Office",
		"Cemetery"
	});
	if (this.Vars.players == 2)
	{
		this.Vars.pointAI = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB
		});
		if (this.Vars.wsuspect == "Butcher's Apprentice")
		{
			this.Vars.hexAI = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"Farmer's Apprentice",
				"Laborer's Union"
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.wsuspect == "Blacksmith's Apprentice")
		{
			this.Vars.hexAI = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"Blacksmith's Apprentice",
				"Laborer's Union"
			});
		}
	}
	else if (this.Vars.players == 3)
	{
		this.Vars.pointAI = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.nameC
		});
		if (this.Vars.wsuspect == "Butcher's Apprentice")
		{
			this.Vars.hexAI = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"Farmer's Apprentice",
				"Laborer's Union"
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.wsuspect == "Blacksmith's Apprentice")
		{
			this.Vars.hexAI = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"Blacksmith's Apprentice",
				"Laborer's Union"
			});
		}
	}
	this.Vars.visit = 0;
	this.Vars.carcount = 0;
	this.Vars.id = 0;
	this.Vars.idA = 0;
	this.Vars.idB = 0;
	this.Vars.idC = 0;
	this.Vars.idD = 0;
	this.Vars.idE = 0;
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage14_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{

{

		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 3)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 4)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC,
				this.Vars.nameD
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 5)

			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC,
				this.Vars.nameD,
				this.Vars.nameE
			});
		}
		this.Vars.randomname = this.Vars.randomplayer;

		yield return base.text(" ");

		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I will keep this letter brief — as brief as I can. You are aware that brevity is not my strongest suit. However, it is August, the ink struggles to dry in the humidity, and my mind is set on complicated things. Perhaps it would be more amiable to pen this missive in my own blood, cold as I am perceived to be by the inhabitants of this gray, lifeless city. It would certainly bring a little more color to it.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("You are probably interested in matters of business, and it is going exceedingly well, or so I hear — I struggle to keep the figures in my head. It appears that my parent's investments have paid off handsomely.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();

It's not that I believe that rehabilitation of the deviant mindset is impossible, it simply requires a more aggressive therapy than they were willing to indulge. With our unmediated assistance and the endorsement of the state, a prison is a more versatile testing ground.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("And I — I am doing well. It disconcerts me. My studies continue with great passion that consumes me more than anything I have ever known. Even the dismal fog that looms across this bleak valley fills me with a solemn peace. Yet it is that same calm which causes my unease.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I must work quickly, as I feel something unseen watches, waiting to emerge from the shadows. I cannot have destiny torn from my grasp just when I reach the pinnacle!");

		yield return base.text("v1.0");
	}

	{
		this.Vars.warden = "The Butcher";
	}
	else
	{
		this.Vars.warden = "The Bloodsmith";
	}

	{
		"Lose 5VP",
		"Discard a Vanity Estate Upgrade from your Estate if possible."
	});
	this.Vars.creepcount = 0;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;

	yield return base.lineBreak();

	yield return base.lineBreak();

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage25_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))

	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.round = 16;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.gen3pg == 0 || this.Vars.gen3pg == "")
	{
		using (base.styleScope("setupStyle", true))
		{
			using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
			{
				yield return base.text("SETUP");
			}
			StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
			this.Vars._SetupImage = "AngryMobSetup1";
			yield return base.lineBreak();
			if (this.Vars.creature == 1)
			{
				yield return base.text("Retrieve the Hunt tokens ");
				yield return base.text("<sprite=\"S2_HuntTokenFRONT\" index=0>");
				yield return base.text(". Turn them all so the yellow crosshairs are face-up.");
				yield return base.lineBreak();
				yield return base.lineBreak();

				yield return base.lineBreak();
			}
			yield return base.text("Place the Suspicion Marker on space ");
			using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
			{
				if (this.Vars.Privatized == 0 || this.Vars.Privatized == "")
				{
					this.Vars.Privatized = 1;
					this.Vars.tracker = int.Parse(this.Vars.tracker) - 1;
					if (this.Vars.players > 3)
					{
						this.Vars.tracker = int.Parse(this.Vars.tracker) - 1;
					}
				}
				yield return base.text(this.Vars.tracker);
			}
			styleScope2 = null;
			yield return base.text(" and the ");
			yield return base.text("<sprite=\"AngryMob_Icon\" index=0>");
			yield return base.text(" Marker one space to the left.");
			yield return base.lineBreak();

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage27_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))

	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.Gen2fate = "creature";
	string text = "Remove all player pieces from the board and perform the End of a Generation. Return any remaining " + this.Vars.asylumup + " tiles to the box. ";
	if (this.Vars.bhome == 0)
	{
		text += "Return the <b>House on the Hill</b> tile to the Scenario box.";
	}
	Action<string, int> s_OnEndOfGeneration = ViewEndOfGeneration.S_OnEndOfGeneration;
	if (s_OnEndOfGeneration != null)
	{
		s_OnEndOfGeneration(text, 6);
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Collected Letters - ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Shelley, Herbert - February 1892.");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.creature == 2)
	{
		yield return base.text("Your previous letter appeared rushed and ended with incoherent scribblings. What is this creature business and why have you failed \"in the eyes of god\" by ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("aiding the poor thing");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text("? Are you quite sure about your own mental state? ");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.text("I have heard a rumor that the ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Asylum has expanded");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(". Perhaps your recent bout of good will spawned this charitable fortune. Whether it is so or not, my friend, I would refer you to it. Not necessarily by way of admitting yourself - unless you feel obliged - but perhaps they could recommend you a remedy to calm your thoughts. I suspect you may require more than a spot of tea and bed rest.");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		this.Vars.Gen2End = "asylum";
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "S4BadCreature", null);
	}
	if (this.Vars.creature == 1)
	{
		yield return base.text("What is this nonsense I hear about a hideous ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("creature left stalking about the countryside");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(" in your region? I ask you only because your recent letters about experiments have been quite unforthcoming.");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.text("I may disagree with your methods, but I have always attempted to stand by you as an academic. 		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.text("This decision has caused people to ");

		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "S4BadCreature", null);
	}

	yield break;

		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.text("As I slept last night, my estate was breached by a stealthy and merciless beast! And when I awoke, it was to an empty bed and the sound of screaming. 		yield return base.lineBreak();

		{
			yield return base.abort("LiberalIntro");
		}
		else

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage42_Main()

			yield return base.text("25 June, 1901.");
		}

	}

	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Peace. The townsfolk use this word so flippantly, it has become tawdry. Can there truly be peace without struggle? What is peace for all when I am not at peace myself?");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("They have come to an agreement. Peace. Our family's actions, they deemed, were not the cause of their ills. 	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();

	}

	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage46_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("The Creature's Demands");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Letter from ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.randomname);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("(Cont.)");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("To my surprise, the hideous monster could speak, his jaw supported by a crudely stitched black thread which exposed the inner muscle when it moved. In deep, guttural tones, he conveyed his hatred for my grandfather, who had created him and abandoned him, helpless in the wild. \"I was forcefully orphaned. Left to fend for myself while his sons and daughters existed in luxury,\" he groaned.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("They say the sins of the father are passed on to the children, but rarely does this obligation skip a full generation. \"You owe me a great debt, and I am here to demand payment,\" he stated firmly, and obstructed my escape until he could finish his tale. I was awestruck by his chilling words and the revelation that our family's dark secrets were indeed a reality.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Cursed into existence despite his decaying form, my grandfather's experiment demanded to live out his days with a faithful companion, another being who can understand the torture of existence. That it was my family's duty to atone for these sins and create it for him!");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("With a final turn, his grotesque figure framed in moonlight, he vowed that if we did not, he would exact a terrible vengeance upon our houses, so that we may know first-hand what torment he has endured!");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "TheCreatureCard", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage54_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Economic Stimulus");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.passage("letter1a", Array.Empty<StoryVar>());
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("As I predicted, the Romanian government's expanding social programs have left it unmercifully poor during this brief recession. I have made protective strides to divert my portfolio abroad, so the impact has been negligible. However, the upheaval caused by this Great War has sparked nationalist sentiments and minor rebellions across Transylvania.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The sudden mantra to protect our own has devolved into a battle within the government. I yawn when I dwell on parliamentary matters for too long. I'm sure it is some endless babble about race, human rights, and religious faith.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The result of this prejudice is that now Transylvania is faced with a dreary decision that has no positive outcome. As landowners and entrepreneurs, naturally, we will make this decision as to how the regional government will proceed.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.players == 2)
	{
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "2PLiberalEvent", null);
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "LiberalEvent1", null);
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;

private void passage58_Init()
{

}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage58_Main()
{
	ViewItemObtain.SetupPassagename = "Foreign";
	if (this.Vars.witch == this.Vars.nameA)
	{
		this.Vars.witch1 = this.Vars.witA;
	}
	else if (this.Vars.witch == this.Vars.nameB)
	{
		this.Vars.witch1 = this.Vars.witB;
	}
	else if (this.Vars.witch == this.Vars.nameC)
	{
		this.Vars.witch1 = this.Vars.witC;
	}
	else if (this.Vars.witch == this.Vars.nameD)
	{
		this.Vars.witch1 = this.Vars.witD;
	}
	else if (this.Vars.witch == this.Vars.nameE)
	{
		this.Vars.witch1 = this.Vars.witE;
	}
	else if (this.Vars.witch == this.Vars.wsuspect)
	{
		this.Vars.witch1 = this.Vars.witAI;
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("setupStyleEvnt", true))
	{
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("SETUP");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
		this.Vars._SetupImage = "S2_WitchHexToken";
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.text("Retrieve the ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Witch's Hex");
		}
		styleScope2 = null;
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("<sprite=\"S2_WitchHexToken\" index=0>");
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("token.");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.text("Place the ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Witch's Hex");
		}
		styleScope2 = null;
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("<sprite=\"S2_WitchHexToken\" index=0>");
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("token on the ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.witch1);
		}
		styleScope2 = null;
		yield return base.text(". This Location is hexed and cannot be visited by any player this round.");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage69_Main()
{
	if (this.Vars.witch == this.Vars.nameA)
	{
		this.Vars.witch2 = this.Vars.witA2;
	}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage81_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Protected Against Witchcraft");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.revresolve == 0)
	{
		string arg = "Remove all player pieces from the board and perform the End of a Generation. Return the Storybook token on space 35 to the supply.";
		Action<string, int> s_OnEndOfGeneration = ViewEndOfGeneration.S_OnEndOfGeneration;
		if (s_OnEndOfGeneration != null)
		{
			s_OnEndOfGeneration(arg, 6);
		}
	}
	else
	{
		string arg2 = "Remove all player pieces from the board and perform the End of a Generation.";
		Action<string, int> s_OnEndOfGeneration2 = ViewEndOfGeneration.S_OnEndOfGeneration;
		if (s_OnEndOfGeneration2 != null)
		{
			s_OnEndOfGeneration2(arg2, 6);
		}
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Newsprint - ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.newspaper);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("13 February, 1891.");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.cursed == 1)
	{
		yield return base.text("Several years have passed since the ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("fatal accusation of ");
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.witch);
		}
		styleScope = null;

{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))

	yield return base.text(this.Vars.townname);
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("for the entirety of its existence. Us. Our family's choices through the generations have had a decisive impact on the history of tensions within the town.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("They were thorough in their assessment. ");
	if (this.Vars.kill == "butcher")
	{
		this.Vars.tensebad = int.Parse(this.Vars.tensebad) + 1;
		yield return base.text("The town's dark history and our grandparents' choice to support the senseless killing of an obviously ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("innocent individual");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(" is noted.");
	}
	else
	{
		this.Vars.tensegood = int.Parse(this.Vars.tensegood) + 1;
		yield return base.text("While frontier justice in the town's history is certainly a negative, our grandparents' choice to hang the ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("guilty party");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(" still resonated.");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.cursed == 2)
	{
		this.Vars.tensebad = int.Parse(this.Vars.tensebad) + 1;
		yield return base.text("Our parents' ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("inability to determine who the cursed witch was");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(" weighed heavily on their minds.");
	}
	else
	{
		this.Vars.tensegood = int.Parse(this.Vars.tensegood) + 1;
		yield return base.text("Successfully ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("unmasking the cursed individual");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(" was seen as a notable element of moral character.");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.walls == "yes")
	{
		this.Vars.tensebad = int.Parse(this.Vars.tensebad) + 1;
		yield return base.text("The Romani remember our misguided decision to ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("provide Strength");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(" to the town.");
	}
	else
	{
		this.Vars.tensegood = int.Parse(this.Vars.tensegood) + 1;
		yield return base.text("The Romani remember that we chose to ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("support Acceptance");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(" and only offered meager support for the town's misguided endeavors.");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The town weighed these options and quickly came to an agreement.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.tensebad > this.Vars.tensegood)
	{
		this.Vars.tension = "bad";
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "ThistenseBad", null);
	}
	else
	{
		this.Vars.tension = "good";
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "ThisTenseGood", null);
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

	this.Vars.isooff = 0;
	if (this.Vars.visit == 0)
	{
		yield return base.abort(this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			"Foreign3",
			"Foreign3",
			"Foreign3",
			"Caravansery"
		}));
	}
	else if (this.Vars.visit == 1)
	{
		if (this.Vars.round == 6)
		{
			yield return base.abort(this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"Isolation",
				"Isolation",
				"Caravansery"
			}));
		}
		if (this.Vars.round == 10)
		{
			yield return base.abort(this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"S4Smug",
				"S4Smug",
				"Caravansery"
			}));
		}
		if (this.Vars.round == 11)
		{
			yield return base.abort(this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"Isolation3",
				"Isolation3",
				"Caravansery"
			}));
		}
	}
	if (this.Vars.visit == 2)
	{
		if (this.Vars.round == 6)
		{
			yield return base.abort(this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"Tension",
				"Tension",
				"Caravansery"
			}));
		}
		if (this.Vars.round == 13)
		{
			yield return base.abort(this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"Tension2",
				"Tension2",
				"Caravansery"
			}));
		}
		if (this.Vars.round == 14)
		{
			yield return base.abort(this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				"Tension3",
				"Tension3",
				"Caravansery"
			}));
		}
	}
	if (this.Vars.visit != 0 && this.Vars.visit != 1 && this.Vars.round != 10 && this.Vars.round != 11 && this.Vars.visit != 2 && this.Vars.round != 13 && this.Vars.round != 14 && this.Vars.round != 6)
	{
		yield return base.abort("Caravansery");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage129_Main()
{

	{
		yield return base.text("Ceaseless Ambition");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.onecount == this.Vars.players)
	{
		this.Vars.fp10vp = 1;
		yield return base.abort("FP1OverBonus");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Choose your player name and begin your destiny:");
	}

			}
			styleScope = null;
		}

	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.players > 4)
	{
		if (this.Vars.Econfirm == 0)

				yield return base.link(this.Vars.nameE, null, () => base.enchantHook("h00168", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage132_Fragment_8), false));

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage138_Main()
{
	this.Vars.fpfate = this.macros1.a(new StoryVar[]
	{
		1,
		2,
		3,
		4,
		5,
		6
	});
	List<int> fpfateList = new List<int>
	{
		1,
		2,
		3,
		4,
		5,
		6
	};
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.fp10vp == 1)
	{
		this.Vars.fpfate = this.Vars.fpfate - this.macros1.a(new StoryVar[]
		{
			1
		});
		fpfateList.Remove(1);
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.fpresearch2 == 1)
	{
		this.Vars.fpfate = this.Vars.fpfate - this.macros1.a(new StoryVar[]
		{
			2
		});
		fpfateList.Remove(2);
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.fpsanity3 == 1)
	{
		this.Vars.fpfate = this.Vars.fpfate - this.macros1.a(new StoryVar[]
		{
			3
		});
		fpfateList.Remove(3);
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.fpcreepy3 == 1)
	{
		this.Vars.fpfate = this.Vars.fpfate - this.macros1.a(new StoryVar[]
		{
			4
		});
		fpfateList.Remove(4);
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.plA == 0)
	{
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		if (fpfateList.Count > 0)
		{
			this.Vars.plA = fpfateList[UnityEngine.Random.Range(0, fpfateList.Count)];
			fpfateList.Remove(this.Vars.plA);
		}
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.plB == 0)
	{
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		if (fpfateList.Count > 0)
		{
			this.Vars.plB = fpfateList[UnityEngine.Random.Range(0, fpfateList.Count)];
			fpfateList.Remove(this.Vars.plB);
		}
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.plC == 0)
	{
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		if (fpfateList.Count > 0)
		{
			this.Vars.plC = fpfateList[UnityEngine.Random.Range(0, fpfateList.Count)];
			fpfateList.Remove(this.Vars.plC);
		}
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.plD == 0)
	{
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		if (fpfateList.Count > 0)
		{
			this.Vars.plD = fpfateList[UnityEngine.Random.Range(0, fpfateList.Count)];
			fpfateList.Remove(this.Vars.plD);
		}
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.plE == 0)
	{
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		if (fpfateList.Count > 0)
		{
			this.Vars.plE = fpfateList[UnityEngine.Random.Range(0, fpfateList.Count)];
		}
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.abort("FPFateAssignHub");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.fp10vp);
	yield return base.text("  ");
	yield return base.text("fame 1");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.fpresearch2);
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("knowledge 2");
	yield return base.lineBreak();

	yield return base.text(" ");

	yield return base.lineBreak();

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage139_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Shared Mania");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Journal Entry - ");
		if (this.Vars.players == 2)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 3)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC
			});
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 4)
		{
			this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				this.Vars.nameA,
				this.Vars.nameB,
				this.Vars.nameC,
				this.Vars.nameD

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage145_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("The Esteemed Institution");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.passage("letter1a", Array.Empty<StoryVar>());
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("If you are not already aware, the new Asylum has begun operations. Naturally, I encountered my dear cousins at the ribbon-cutting ceremony just weeks ago. As was customary during these sorts of celebrations, the mayor of ");
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.townname);
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("was dolefully in attendance, as were several visiting dignitaries of various unimportance.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("If it weren't enough to stunt my studies with niceties, the event that followed a few days later served to compound my annoyance with this pseudoscience. One of my servants had willingly admitted themselves to this untested facility! And after all the care I had given them!");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I fear I will be forced to visit this place now. Perhaps the introduction of these alienist philosophies will soothe my anxieties. Ha! I chortled so hard at that I nearly spilt my brandy upon the page.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("hook", "h000145"))
	{
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", null, () => base.enchantHook("h000145", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage145_Fragment_0), false));
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage152_Main()
{
	if (this.Vars.Av > 1)
	{
		yield return base.abort("AsylumComplete");
	}
	if (this.Vars.Bv > 1)
	{
		yield return base.abort("AsylumComplete");
	}
	if (this.Vars.Cv > 1)
	{
		yield return base.abort("AsylumComplete");
	}
	if (this.Vars.Dv > 1)
	{
		yield return base.abort("AsylumComplete");
	}
	if (this.Vars.Ev > 1)
	{
		yield return base.abort("AsylumComplete");
	}
	else
	{
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Retrieval of Property");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope = null;
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.tempas);
			yield return base.text("'s Journal - ");
			using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
			{
				yield return base.passage("date1a", Array.Empty<StoryVar>());
			}
			StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
		}
		styleScope = null;

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage153_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Total Contributions");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The Asylum received a total of ");
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("$");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.asylumcount);
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("in donations.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The Count received a total of ");
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("$");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.businesscount);
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("in donations.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.asylumcount == this.Vars.businesscount)
	{
		this.Vars.asylumcount = int.Parse(this.Vars.asylumcount) + 1;
		yield return base.text("The funds offered were equal. This indecisiveness will result in our perceived support for treatment.");
	}
	else if (this.Vars.businesscount > this.Vars.asylumcount)
	{
		this.Vars.jail = 2;
		yield return base.text("The Count will be pleased.");
	}
	else
	{
		this.Vars.jail = 1;
		yield return base.text("Hopefully this support will strengthen our relationship with the Asylum.");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "S4CountCure", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

	if (this.Vars.Ccont == 0)
	{
		if (this.Vars.players > 3)
		{
			yield return base.abort("Payment1D");
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 3)
		{
			yield return base.abort("Payment1Hub");
		}
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Carefully hand this Storybook device to ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameC);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("and do not allow any other players to see the screen.");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("hook", "h000167"))
	{
		yield return base.link("Once you are ready, click here to reveal your secret conversation.", null, () => base.enchantHook("h000167", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage167_Fragment_1), false));
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

	{
		ViewItemObtain.SetupPassagename = "Payment1D";
	}
	if (this.Vars.players == 3)
	{
		ViewItemObtain.SetupPassagename = "Payment1Hub";
	}
	using (base.styleScope("setupStyleEvnt", true))
	{
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("SETUP");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
		this.Vars._SetupImage = "Money_Icon";
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Immediately pay $");
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.Ccont);
			yield return base.text(" ");
			yield return base.text("to the supply.");
		}
		styleScope2 = null;
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	this.Vars.Ccont = 0;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private void passage174_Init()
{
	base.Passages["JailEvent1"] = new StoryPassage("JailEvent1", new string[0], new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage174_Main));
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage174_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("The Escape");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Letter from ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.randomname);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("(Cont.)");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I met with their leader just days previous, through coercive means I assure you. There I was, forced to mingle with criminals and rust-covered sociopaths in coveralls, bruised and thrust upon the steps of the prison, or what they now call the Junk Palace.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.kill == "blacksmith")
	{
		yield return base.text("A man stepped forward to the cheers of a throng of miscreants. The man was strong and rough with a ruddy complexion, a broad, square jaw, and a beard separated by deep scars along his cheeks. He wore a thick apron with one shoulder strap ripped at the seams. The front was covered in dark stains, and by his confident stride, he seemed to revel in its uncleanliness. In his gloved hand, he held a hammer which dripped with a red substance that also stained his fingers.");
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.text("A woman stepped forward to the cheers of a throng of miscreants. Her hair was cropped shorter than a bob, dark and wild with a sheen of oil. It framed her angular face and draped over a black eye-patch that covered her left eye. She wore a thick apron that was once white, but now stained a dark crimson with fresh droplets of red bespattered across the chest. In her gloved hand, she held a metal cleaver, rusted near the handle, with thick divots in the blade from years of use.");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("\"They call me ");
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.warden);
	yield return base.text(". Perhaps you remember my family, and how they were ruined by the accusations of hysterical peons so many generations ago. Well now, us unfortunate wretches have taken back what is rightfully ours. ");
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.warden);
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("runs this town.\"");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The aberrant horde roared their approval. The malcontented rabble beat their chests and clattered metal upon metal. ");
	if (this.Vars.creature == 1 && this.Vars.exped == 0)
	{
		yield return base.text("I spied a shadowy figure within the Junk Palace, its distorted silhouette framed against the entryway for a moment before disappearing once again. Was this the same creature I had hunted for?");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("\"I have brought you here because you are useful. But mark my words, ");
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.warden);
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("expects loyalty.\"");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "JailEvent1A", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private void passage175_Init()

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage182_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("A Note for my Sister");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Roderick Tenderson - ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("1932.");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I have made much progress in my research over these last months. My host has furnished me with appropriate accommodations and the food is hearty with a warmth that lifts the spirits. While I am gracious for their hospitality, I have yet to give my appreciation in person. The caretaker assures me that they are on extended holiday, but their absence is peculiar. Something about this arrangement unnerves me, though I cannot for the life of me determine its source.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("It is but a minor xenophobia, a fear of the unknown that sets my eyes to dwelling on the dark corners of this unfamiliar, decaying, but immaculate estate. At night, I perceive to hear the echoes of a distant hammering, the scraping of metal on metal, the rumble of thunder. Yet when I sash my nightgown tight and emerge upon the veranda, the misty countryside is spread wide under the moon and I am greeted with nothing but the echo of cicadas and the smell of tulips in the night air.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The business at hand: Included within the accompanying package is an extensive collection of clippings, journal entries, and letters chronicling the storied history of this peculiar estate and its proprietors. Their contents are fascinating and I have arranged them in a semblance of order which tells a vivid, extraordinary tale.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I expect to return to London shortly, but I have posted this ahead of my arrival so as to make the burden lighter for me. I fear I don't have the same fortitude that I once did. If perchance something were to happen to me, I trust you will ensure its publication in whatever form you see fit.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("As always, I think of you fondly. Give mother my warmest regards.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Roderick");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.players == 2)
	{
		this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB
		});
	}
	if (this.Vars.players == 3)
	{
		this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.nameC
		});
	}
	if (this.Vars.players == 4)
	{
		this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.nameC,
			this.Vars.nameD
		});
	}
	if (this.Vars.players == 5)
	{
		this.Vars.randomplayer = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.nameA,
			this.Vars.nameB,
			this.Vars.nameC,
			this.Vars.nameD,
			this.Vars.nameE
		});
	}
	yield return base.link("Click to continue...", "FearoftheUnknownStart", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

		});

	}

	{
		this.Vars.plotB = "yes";

	{
		this.Vars.plotC = "yes";
	}

	{
		this.Vars.plotD = "yes";
	}
	if (this.Vars.tempplot == this.Vars.nameE)
	{
		this.Vars.plotE = "yes";
	}
	if (this.Vars.round == 1)
	{
		yield return base.abort("Mania");
	}
	else if (this.Vars.round == 2)
	{
		yield return base.abort("Mania2");
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.abort("Mania3");
	}
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage209_Main()
{

	}

		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();

	yield return base.text("It feels like ages since I have written. The village that we once sojourned to all those years ago has fallen silent. It's crumbling defenses are a reminder; a metaphor for the crippling isolation of xenophobia. Even now I remember those accursed city walls that sapped my youthful vitality with every visit into the murky depths of that place; a place that could never be rebuilt after the hideous Experiment was unleashed.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Yet, even now the indomitable pull of my family's infamous work tears at my very soul! No. I cannot carry on a legacy of fear that left an entire town and estate in ruins. My colleagues at the university have no reverence for me. They laugh so heartily when I tell them the town in which I was birthed. I do not blame them. My hope is that I shall never see that foul place again. How could my family cultivate such an embarrassing line of thinking?");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("As I pen this note, my lawyer has made arrangements for a transfer of ownership; the deed to that wretched estate will soon finally be wrested from my hands and with it, the insidious efforts contained within will be buried forever.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("THE END?");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage212_Fragment_0()
{
	this.Vars.id = int.Parse(this.Vars.id) + 1;
	if (this.Vars.tempid == this.Vars.nameA)
	{
		this.Vars.idA = "yes";
	}
	if (this.Vars.tempid == this.Vars.nameB)
	{
		this.Vars.idB = "yes";
	}
	if (this.Vars.tempid == this.Vars.nameC)
	{
		this.Vars.idC = "yes";
	}
	if (this.Vars.tempid == this.Vars.nameD)
	{
		this.Vars.idD = "yes";
	}
	if (this.Vars.tempid == this.Vars.nameE)
	{
		this.Vars.idE = "yes";
	}
	if (this.Vars.round == 10)
	{
		yield return base.abort("Isolation");
	}
	else if (this.Vars.round == 11)
	{
		yield return base.abort("Isolation2");
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.abort("Isolation3");
	}
	yield break;
}

	else if (this.Vars.nameB == this.Vars.fate2)
	{
		yield return base.text("My thirst for knowledge is unquenchable. Each evening I search through ancient tomes and scholarly texts, scouring every printed word and mathematical formula as if it were the last I will ever read.");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}

	{

		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	else if (this.Vars.nameB == this.Vars.fate4)
	{
		yield return base.text("I am surrounded by simple-minded human filth. How dare they look at such an affluent individual with judgement in their eyes? How dare they interfere with an aristocrat's greatest, most valuable work? Oh, they will PAY for their insolence!");

		yield return base.lineBreak();

	else if (this.Vars.nameB == this.Vars.fate5)
	{
		yield return base.text("I will not suffer fools. It is just as important for a peasant or a king to know their place in the presence of my genius. I will show them ");

		{
			yield return base.text("all");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(" how to pay homage to their betters. Soon there will be no way to ignore my inspirational presence and I will command respect!");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	else

		yield return base.text("I find pleasure in the simple act of experimentation. Every tested hypothesis is a delectable morsel to be savored. And is it not my obligation - my right - to share this sense of wonder with the world? The wretches deserve to be entertained - for what is life without spectacle and indulgence?");

		yield return base.lineBreak();

	{
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", null, () => base.enchantHook("h0000355", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage355_Fragment_0), false));

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage356_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameC);
		yield return base.text("'s Obsession");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Journal of ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameC);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.passage("date1a", Array.Empty<StoryVar>());
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.nameC == this.Vars.fate1)
	{
		yield return base.text("My lust for fame knows no boundaries. Whether fulfilled through ethical means or the mark of infamy, I was born with a yearning to be known both far and wide for my scientific exploits. These narcissistic thoughts plague my waking hours and infect my dreams!");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	else if (this.Vars.nameC == this.Vars.fate2)
	{
		yield return base.text("My thirst for knowledge is unquenchable. Each evening I search through ancient tomes and scholarly texts, scouring every printed word and mathematical formula as if it were the last I will ever read.");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	else if (this.Vars.nameC == this.Vars.fate3)
	{
		yield return base.text("I have spent days upon days locked away within my secret laboratory. It is as though my entire existence is singularly focused on the pursuit of scientific excellence. I do not care if it drives me mad! If my contributions can advance Science even by a minute amount it will all be worth it!");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	else if (this.Vars.nameC == this.Vars.fate4)
	{
		yield return base.text("I am surrounded by simple-minded human filth. How dare they look at such an affluent individual with judgement in their eyes? How dare they interfere with an aristocrat's greatest, most valuable work? Oh, they will PAY for their insolence!");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	else if (this.Vars.nameC == this.Vars.fate5)
	{
		yield return base.text("I will not suffer fools. It is just as important for a peasant or a king to know their place in the presence of my genius. I will show them ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("all");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(" how to pay homage to their betters. Soon there will be no way to ignore my inspirational presence and I will command respect!");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.text("I find pleasure in the simple act of experimentation. Every tested hypothesis is a delectable morsel to be savored. And is it not my obligation - my right - to share this sense of wonder with the world? The wretches deserve to be entertained - for what is life without spectacle and indulgence?");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	using (base.styleScope("hook", "h0000356"))
	{
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", null, () => base.enchantHook("h0000356", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage356_Fragment_0), false));

	}

	{

			yield return base.text(text.Replace("_1", ""));
		}
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("Complete");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Agility: ");
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.agiA);
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Strength: ");
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.strA);
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Life: ");
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.hitA);
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("You are ready for a trial by combat!");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();

	yield return base.text(temptTarget.Replace("_1", "").Replace("_2", "").Replace("_3", "").Replace("_4", "").Replace("_5", ""));
	yield return base.text(".");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.active == this.Vars.warriorA)
	{
		this.Vars.tempstr = this.Vars.strA;
	}
	else if (this.Vars.active == this.Vars.warriorB)
	{
		this.Vars.tempstr = this.Vars.strB;
	}

	{
		this.Vars.tempstr = this.Vars.strC;
	}

	{
		this.Vars.tempstr = this.Vars.strD;
	}
	else if (this.Vars.active == this.Vars.warriorE)
	{
		this.Vars.tempstr = this.Vars.strE;
	}
	if (this.Vars.target == this.Vars.warriorA)
	{
		this.Vars.tempagi = this.Vars.agiA;
	}

	{
		this.Vars.tempagi = this.Vars.agiB;

	{
		this.Vars.tempagi = this.Vars.agiD;
	}

	{
		this.Vars.tempagi = this.Vars.agiE;
	}
	if (this.macros1.random(1.0, 40.0) > this.Vars.tempagi)
	{
		yield return base.text(temptTarget.Replace("_1", "").Replace("_2", "").Replace("_3", "").Replace("_4", "").Replace("_5", ""));

			this.Vars.temphit = this.Vars.hitA;

			this.Vars.warriorB
		});
	}
	else if (this.Vars.players == 3)
	{
		this.Vars.elim = this.macros1.a(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.warriorA,
			this.Vars.warriorB,
			this.Vars.warriorC
		});
	}
	else if (this.Vars.players == 4)
	{
		this.Vars.elim = this.macros1.a(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.warriorA,
			this.Vars.warriorB,
			this.Vars.warriorC,
			this.Vars.warriorD
		});
	}
	else
	{
		this.Vars.elim = this.macros1.a(new StoryVar[]
		{
			this.Vars.warriorA,
			this.Vars.warriorB,
			this.Vars.warriorC,
			this.Vars.warriorD,
			this.Vars.warriorE
		});
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.elim = this.macros1.shuffled(new StoryVar[]
	{
		(HarloweSpread)this.Vars.elim
	});
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.active = this.Vars.elim["1st"];
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.target = this.Vars.elim["2nd"];
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.abort("BattleStart");
	yield break;
}

	{
		yield return base.abort("BusMeetA");
	}
	else if (this.Vars.busm == this.Vars.nameB)
	{
		yield return base.abort("BusMeetB");
	}
	else if (this.Vars.busm == this.Vars.nameC)
	{
		yield return base.abort("BusMeetC");
	}
	else if (this.Vars.busm == this.Vars.nameD)
	{
		yield return base.abort("BusMeetD");
	}
	else if (this.Vars.busm == this.Vars.nameE)
	{
		yield return base.abort("BusMeetE");
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.abort("BusMeetA");
	}
	yield break;
}

		yield return base.text(this.Vars.cureplayer);
	}

	yield return base.lineBreak();

	yield return base.lineBreak();

		yield return base.text("The Expedition Uncovers...");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("If the number of Clue symbols ");
	yield return base.text("<sprite=\"S2_HuntTokenBACKRED\" index=0>");
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("collected is equal to ");
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		if (this.Vars.round == 16 || this.Vars.round == 19)
		{
			yield return base.text(7 - int.Parse(this.macros1.random(1.0, 4.0)));
		}
		else if (this.Vars.round == 17 || this.Vars.round == 20)
		{
			yield return base.text(7 - int.Parse(this.macros1.random(1.0, 5.0)));
		}
		else
		{
			yield return base.text(7 - int.Parse(this.macros1.random(1.0, 6.0)));
		}
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("or more, the Creature is found and the hunt is a success. Otherwise, the hunt is unsuccessful.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Were you successful in finding the Creature?");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("Yes.", "ExpYes", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.link("No.", "ExpNo", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage261_Main()
{
	if (this.ispopup)
	{
		this.ispopup = false;
		ViewPopupPanel.instance.Clear();
		ViewPopupPanel.instance.OnGenerationBtn("LiberalEvent3Resa", "Please enter the name of your new rehabilitation program:", "string", 0.5f);
	}
	else if (ViewPopupPanel.instance.PassageValueString() != null)
	{
		this.Vars.menname = ViewPopupPanel.instance.PassageValueString();
		this.ispopup = true;
		ViewPopupPanel.instance.Clear();
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("The ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.menname);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("Program");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Newsprint - ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.newspaper);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("27 February, 1902.");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The Asylum has announced a radical change to their rehabilitative efforts, incorporating the most advanced alienist treatment regimen. ");
	if (this.Vars.mentype == "Engineering")
	{
		yield return base.text("A new wing of the facility displays the complex machinery utilized in this fascinating new therapy. Patients with varying degrees of dementia are carefully strapped to a hospital bed, while electrical pulses are concentrated upon different areas of the brain.");
	}
	else if (this.Vars.mentype == "Chemistry")
	{
		yield return base.text("Using new advances in concentrated opiates, the doctors are able to administer strong sedatives to alleviate improper reflexes in patients. Through a combination of bloodletting and strong purgatives, the psychotic tendencies of the individual are allowed to exit the body.");
	}
	else if (this.Vars.mentype == "Biology")
	{
		yield return base.text("An entirely rebuilt surgical stage has been constructed where visiting physicians and the public alike can view the procedures as they are perfected. By removing the offending portions of brain tissue, or by alleviating pressures in the skull, the mentally ill experience a transformative effect which renders them placid and focused.");
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.text("While officials remain tight-lipped as to the details of the procedure, a bishop of the local diocese has been given residence to perform blessings to those whose will has been overcome by demons. Patients are isolated from stimulation, prescribed a \"rest cure,\" and given a special restorative tonic of local roots and herbs.");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("While critics of the hospital remain outspoken, the progressive organization has embraced this change as proof that ");
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.townname);
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("remains the most modern psychiatric refuge in all of Transylvania.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("hook", "h000261"))
	{
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", null, () => base.enchantHook("h000261", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage261_Fragment_0), false));
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

	yield return base.lineBreak();

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage276_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Peace in Defiance");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	ViewGenerationEnding.instance.EnableDisableContinueBtn(true);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Journal Entry - ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.winner);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- 16 August, 1929");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Sunday: I had the glorious dream again - it never fails to reinvigorate me, as I could relive that moment each night for the remainder of my years and be content.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I watch with steady eyes as my family's creation, ");
	if (this.Vars.winner == this.Vars.nameA)
	{
		string text = this.Vars.warriorA.ToString();
		yield return base.text(text.Replace("_1", ""));
	}
	else if (this.Vars.winner == this.Vars.nameB)
	{
		string text2 = this.Vars.warriorB.ToString();
		yield return base.text(text2.Replace("_2", ""));
	}
	else if (this.Vars.winner == this.Vars.nameC)
	{
		string text3 = this.Vars.warriorC.ToString();
		yield return base.text(text3.Replace("_3", ""));
	}
	else if (this.Vars.winner == this.Vars.nameD)
	{
		string text4 = this.Vars.warriorD.ToString();
		yield return base.text(text4.Replace("_4", ""));
	}
	else if (this.Vars.winner == this.Vars.nameE)
	{
		string text5 = this.Vars.warriorE.ToString();
		yield return base.text(text5.Replace("_5", ""));
	}
	else
	{
		string text6 = this.Vars.warriorA.ToString();
		yield return base.text(text6.Replace("_1", ""));
	}
	yield return base.text(", with cathartic ambivalence, lifts the severed head of ");
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.warden);
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("high into the air. I feel the searing heat of burning oil, hear the hiss of rising steam and smoke, and smell the rusted iron in the air. The crowded arena cheered even as their leader was torn from his makeshift throne and tossed lifeless to the dusty Earth, blood pooling beneath, dark and thick as motor oil.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("These images appear in my mind like light on silver even as my weathered hands strain to grasp the quill. My last act of defiance, perhaps. But what is the worth of toppling a regional tyrant? All this effort to shake the world, and barely one square kilometer has been rattled.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The inmates have moved on. The town is an empty, ruined field without vegetation; a decaying pile of ash, rust, and mud. Some days my mind feels the same. The sense of peace does nothing to stem this emptiness of purpose inside of me. ");
	if (this.Vars.creature == 2)
	{
		yield return base.text("An old man visits now and then; a friend of the family with a withered face that he keeps wrapped tightly with a scarf.");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("What a waste contentment is! What a terrible investment! I only hope my progeny will leave this broken land behind and forge a new path.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("THE END?");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage282_Main()
{

			yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameA);
			yield return base.text(" loses ");
			using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
			{

			}
			styleScope = null;
			yield return base.text(" and must discard an Estate Upgrade to the box.");
			yield return base.lineBreak();
		}
		if (this.Vars.idB == 0 || this.Vars.idB == "")
		{
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameB);
			yield return base.text(" loses ");
			using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
			{

			}
			styleScope = null;
			yield return base.text(" and must discard an Estate Upgrade to the box.");
			yield return base.lineBreak();
		}
		if ((this.Vars.idC == 0 || this.Vars.idC == "") && this.Vars.players >= 3)
		{
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameC);
			yield return base.text(" loses ");
			using (base.styleScope("bold", true))

			yield return base.text(" loses ");

			yield return base.lineBreak();
		}
		if ((this.Vars.idE == 0 || this.Vars.idE == "") && this.Vars.players >= 5)

			yield return base.text(" loses ");

			yield return base.text("All other players have completed their required verification and no penalty is assessed.");

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage291_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Junkyard Scrap");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Journal Entry: ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.tempname);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.passage("date1a", Array.Empty<StoryVar>());
		}
		StyleScope styleScope2 = null;
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	this.Vars.creepcount = int.Parse(this.Vars.creepcount) + 1;
	this.Vars.pripg = 1;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("\"What a joy it is to see your soul laid bare,\" ");
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.warden);
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("said to me while gazing out a nearby window in the broken mess hall. The iron grate on the opening had been torn from the concrete and left mangled and exposed to the elements. It cast a twisted shadow across the stone floor. \"I see that you are a monster by nature. And one cannot be blamed for simply following one's natural impulses.\"");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("I was stunned by the insinuation, but as ");
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.warden);
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("raised ");
	if (this.Vars.warden == "The Butcher")
	{
		yield return base.text("her cleaver into the air and pointed it in my direction, I kept my objection to myself. She continued.");
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.text("his hammer and pounded it into his open palm, I remained silent. He continued.");
	}
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("\"Your fate is sealed and you are not to be forgiven, but you will be rewarded for what I have seen. And I will remember.\"");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("It was then that I was offered a choice that I did not expect and pondered on my carriage ride home. This patronizing generosity vexed me, but the words echoed in my mind.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Had I truly become a monster? Or was ");
	yield return base.text(this.Vars.warden);
	yield return base.text(" ");

	yield return base.lineBreak();

	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.strB);
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Life: ");
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.hitB);
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("You are ready for a trial by combat!");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("If this is correct, please ");
	yield return base.link("click to continue...", "Player3StatEntry", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();

	yield return base.link("return to the start...", "Player2StatEntry", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage320_Main()
{
	if (this.Vars.Ccont == 0)
	{
		if (this.Vars.players > 3)
		{
			yield return base.abort("PaymentOrDeathD");
		}
		if (this.Vars.players == 3)
		{
			yield return base.abort("Payment2Hub");
		}
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Carefully hand this Storybook device to ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameC);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("and do not allow any other players to see the screen.");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("hook", "h000320"))
	{
		yield return base.link("Once you are ready, click here to reveal your secret conversation.", null, () => base.enchantHook("h000320", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage320_Fragment_1), false));
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield break;
	yield break;
}
