	using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("(Ties are broken by the player who was last in turn order the previous round).");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("YAY");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("- A vote for ");

	{
		yield return base.text("YAY");
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("is a vote to increase taxes. ");
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))

	}

				yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameA);
			}

		}

			}
			styleScope = null;

		}

		if (this.Vars.players >= 3)
		{
			if (this.Vars.creepC == 0 || this.Vars.creepC == "")
			{
				using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
				{
					yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameC);

			}

			{
				using (base.styleScope("bold", true))

					yield return base.text(this.Vars.nameD);
				}
				styleScope = null;
				yield return base.text(" must suffer the penalty below.");

		}

	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();

	{
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.text("The ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.wsuspect);
		yield return base.text(" can also be chosen by pointing at the Village Chronicle. The ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.wsuspect);
		yield return base.text(" will reveal their accusation after this initial vote concludes.");
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("The starting player will now count down from 3 to 0. On the count of zero, all players must simultaneously point a finger at the player they believe to be the witch.");
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("Keep those fingers pointed and ");
	yield return base.link("click here...", "Witchres1", null);
	yield return base.lineBreak();

	yield break;

	yield return base.lineBreak();

	if (this.Vars.question == this.Vars.cureplayer)
	{
		yield return base.text("The patient is perfectly physically and mentally fit. I find absolutely nothing wrong with such a fine specimen of completely normal human breedstock and am utterly confused as to why they were admitted! Such sharp teeth, such glorious pallor, such divine form; why I wish all patients were so adequately equipped.");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	else if (this.Vars.test >= 3)
	{
		yield return base.text("Alas, despite such a ");
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("healthy");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text("candidate for mental reformation, I must admit that they are too instrumental in the region to be confined to such dismal environs. No, I must satiate myself, and the Asylum, with others who are afflicted ");
		using (base.styleScope("italic", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("(and less important)");
		}
		styleScope = null;
		yield return base.text(". Release has thereby been procured upon certain private matters being addressed. It is my hope that they will provide a suitable referral in their stead.");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.text("Uggh. ");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.text("Perhaps it is unprofessional to pen my disgust upon the page, but this patient is completely undesirable for admittance. Or might I say, unfit for our institute's psychological consumption. Still, it is imperative that I negotiate the matter with the to-be-released ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.question);
		yield return base.text(" as I find myself unsatiated by this meager assessment. I am sure a referral to our glorious facility will suffice. Perhaps they know of one who is afflicted by instability - perhaps one well-fed, with rosy cheeks, and warm blood flowing through their veins.");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("hook", "h0000360"))
	{
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", null, () => base.enchantHook("h0000360", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage360_Fragment_0), false));
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage378_Main()
{
	using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
	{
		yield return base.text("Patient ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.question);
		yield return base.text(" ");
		yield return base.text("- Assessment Results");
	}
	StyleScope styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.text("After completion of a full mental evaluation, a basal metabolism test was conducted, indicating ");
	yield return base.text(this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
	{
		"an abnormally low result which could be symptomatic of disease in the endocrine and nervous system.",
		"a reasonably low result which is usually accompanied by low blood pressure and general malaise.",
		"no statistically significant variation.",
		"a slightly higher result which could be dietary in nature.",
		"an abnormally high percentage of carbon dioxide production sometimes associated with agitated and aggressive behavior."
	}));
	yield return base.text(" ");
	yield return base.text("This was accompanied by a standard physical examination which revealed ");
	yield return base.text(this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
	{
		"minor signs of malnutrition, dehydration, and ruddy complexion, usually associated with stressful events.",
		"a healthy individual within the typical ranges considered as normal.",
		"nothing particularly concerning or outside of the norm aside from several chemical burn marks across the forearms.",
		"signs of obesity due to a life of sedentary indulgence common amongst the upper-middle class."
	}));
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	if (this.Vars.test <= 3)
	{
		if (this.Vars.AsylumTestResultsnextpsg == "" || this.Vars.AsylumTestResultsnextpsg == 0)
		{
			this.Vars.AsylumTestResultsnextpsg = this.macros1.either(new StoryVar[]
			{
				1,
				2,
				3,
				4,
				5
			});
		}
		this.Vars.outcome = this.Vars.AsylumTestResultsnextpsg;
		if (this.Vars.outcome == 1)
		{
			yield return base.text("It is of my informed opinion that patient ");
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.question);
			yield return base.text(" should receive continued evaluation over the coming years. This can be achieved by infrequent visitations by a physician. Full release dependent upon ");
			using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
			{
				yield return base.text("payment of $1");
			}
			styleScope = null;
			yield return base.text(".");
			yield return base.lineBreak();
			yield return base.lineBreak();
		}
		if (this.Vars.outcome == 2)
		{
			yield return base.text("Patient ");
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.question);
			yield return base.text(" has been admitted for static electro-therapy and is progressing towards full release in the coming weeks. Prescribed laudanum and phosphates for nerves. Recommend bed rest and mild sedation. Patient severely disputes this prescriptive inaction.");
			yield return base.lineBreak();
			yield return base.lineBreak();
		}
		if (this.Vars.outcome == 3)
		{
			yield return base.text("I have offered training to a close associate of patient ");
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.question);
			yield return base.text(", in order to assist with specified home care upon release. Subject's behavior and mental state is erratic enough to warrant vigilant supervision. While this caretaker's visage suggests that they may also benefit from psychoanalysis, I am satisfied by their dedication and promise to provide the utmost care to ");
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.question);
			yield return base.text(".");
			yield return base.lineBreak();
			yield return base.lineBreak();
		}
		if (this.Vars.outcome == 4)
		{
			yield return base.text("After several aggressive outbursts while confined, patient ");
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.question);
			yield return base.text(" has been restrained during the evenings to prevent possible self-harm. I have consulted with members of the Vienna Psychoanalytic Society and their analysis implies deep-seated sexual repression manifesting in dissociative behavior. We are proceeding with an operation to sterilize the patient. This should have the combined effect of reducing a drive towards the destruction of self and others.");
			yield return base.lineBreak();
			yield return base.lineBreak();
		}
		if (this.Vars.outcome == 5)
		{
			yield return base.text("It appears patient ");
			yield return base.text(this.Vars.question);
			yield return base.text(" has no physical or noticeable mental deficiencies, though their demeanor is forceful at times. Ailment is assumed to be psychological in nature, possibly brought about by recent stresses. I have recommended heroin for treatment, as it is readily available, non-addictive, and reasonably priced. Perhaps the relaxing effects will also provide respite.");
			yield return base.lineBreak();
			yield return base.lineBreak();
		}
	}
	else
	{
		yield return base.text("Patient ");
		yield return base.text(this.Vars.question);
		yield return base.text(" has been admitted to the Asylum for permanent residency. It is my belief that even temporary release of an individual with such strong psychotic tendencies would be a disservice to mankind. But for the grace of god, I see no possible end to this mental affliction. The only conscionable course of action is to refuse them the ability to enact their horrible schemes. ");
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	using (base.styleScope("hook", "h000037800"))
	{
		yield return base.link("Click to continue...", null, () => base.enchantHook("h000037800", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, new Func<IEnumerable<StoryOutput>>(this.passage378_Fragment_0), false));
	}
	styleScope = null;
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}

private IEnumerable<StoryOutput> passage379_Main()
{
	if (this.Vars.next == 1)
	{
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Assessment Question No. 1");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope = null;
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.passage(this.Vars.quest1, Array.Empty<StoryVar>());
	}
	if (this.Vars.next == 2)
	{
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Assessment Question No. 2");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope = null;
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.passage(this.Vars.quest2, Array.Empty<StoryVar>());
	}
	if (this.Vars.next == 3)
	{
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Assessment Question No. 3");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope = null;
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.passage(this.Vars.quest3, Array.Empty<StoryVar>());
	}
	if (this.Vars.next == 4)
	{
		using (base.styleScope("bold", true))
		{
			yield return base.text("Assessment Question No. 4");
		}
		StyleScope styleScope = null;
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.lineBreak();
		yield return base.passage(this.Vars.quest4, Array.Empty<StoryVar>());
	}
	if (this.Vars.next == 5)
	{
		if (this.Vars.curecount == "yes")
		{
			yield return base.abort("CountTestResults");
		}
		else
		{
			yield return base.abort("AsylumTestResults");
		}
	}
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield return base.lineBreak();
	yield break;
	yield break;
}
